  <brief_title>Does Lung Impedance Correlate With Changes in BNP in Stable and Acutely Decompensated Heart Failure Patients?</brief_title>
  <acronym>IMPEDE-HF</acronym>
  <official_title>Does Lung Impedance Correlate With Changes in BNP in Stable and Acutely Decompensated Heart Failure Patients?</official_title>
